Governor Samuel Ortom of Benue State, on Thursday terminated the appointment of Mr Mike Idoko as the Vice Chairman, Lobi Stars Football Club. This was contained in a statement issued in Makurdi by the Secretary to the State Government, SSG, Prof Anthony A Ijohor. According to the statement, the termination of Idokoâ€™s appointment takes immediate effect. The statement also directed Mr Idoko to hand over all Government properties in his possession to the Secretary of the club. Prof Anthony A Ijohor, in the statement, expressed appreciation to Mr Mike Idoko for the services rendered to the state while in office and wished him well in his future endeavours.